Hindu religious figure of the type known as <a href="/wiki/Avatar" title="Avatar">avatar</a>, godman (pg 583)</li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> Nagel, Alexandra (note: Nagel is a critical former follower) "Een mysterieuze ontmoeting...&#160;:Sai Baba en mentalist Wolf Messing" published in <i>Tijdschrift voor Parapsychologie</i> 368, vol. 72 nr 4, December 2005, pp. 14-17 <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Dutch)</span><br />
